songs.title: Wish
songs.lyrics:
Dear, do not you see that I give you the whole world?

My dear, everything I do is for you, I'm dying for you
You do not know what I would give, I would kill for you
Do you want to see our children grow? I do it for them
I want to make a wish, I want to ask you ...

Honey, come with me to sing, let us sleep, I would do it for you
You know, there are thousands of ways to tell you that I love you
I'm going to say it as many times as necessary, you know

I know this is real, I am very different from others
At least that's what you say, I do not want to be different
I want to be like I want, I want to be like that, I love you
